properties.notes: On 2 November 2023, Hezbollah forces fired missiles from Lebanon toward northern Israel, causing sirens to sound in Kiryat Shmona (Zefat, HaZafon) and surrounding areas. Hamas claimed responsibility for firing 12 rockets from Lebanon in the direction Kiryat Shmona. Hezbollah was responsible for the rest of the rocket fire from Lebanon.
